description: Enferno Storm Commerce API Client library.
releaseNotes:
What's new?

      ExportService:
      - #809 Added PriceListSeed to ListProductItems and ListProducts. New ExportHelper with support for this will be available in StormApiClient nuget when released.
      - #812 Added CultureCode to ListProductItems and ListProducts. New ExportHelper with support for this will be available in StormApiClient nuget when released.

      OrderService:
      - #182, #794 Added TypeId to order. TypeId = 1 is for normal orders and TypeId = 3 is for orders from Subscriptions.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Orders/Entities/Order

      ProductService:  
      - #846 SortOrder has been added to FilterItem. This applies to parametric filters with list values or multi values and enables sorting on the values in client applications. Default sort order is Name.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Products/Entities/FilterItem

      - #819 ProductImages are now sorted by FileInfo.SortOrder. This is not yet implemented in StormAdmin.

      ShoppingService:
      - #706 New method, ListBasketItemInfoTypes.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Shopping/Operations/ListBasketItemInfoTypes


      What's fixed?

      OrderService:
      - #400 OrderItem now has Type and ImageKey mapped correctly.

      ShoppingService:
      - #660 GetCheckout now returns correct status on Basket after purchase has completed.
       

      Miscellaneous changes? 

      N/A

      Feedback?
      Faults and strange behavior can be reported to support@storm.io or to patrik.rosquist@storm.io.
       
       
      Regards,
      The Storm API Team
title: Enferno Storm Api Client
